Interface TypedEntityContainer<T>

Type Parameters:
T - State type.
All Superinterfaces:
Container<TypedEntity<T>>, EntityContainer<T,TypedEntity<T>>, Resource<TypedEntity<T>>, TypedResource<T>
All Known Implementing Classes:
EphemeralEntityContainer
public interface TypedEntityContainer<T> extends EntityContainer<T,TypedEntity<T>>, TypedResource<T>
Binds EntityContainer to T and TypedEntity<T>. This interface is intended to abstract clients from different implementations of typed entities and containers.

Pavel
